rious procedural lapses in actions against dangerous buildings. Ward officials are warned of disciplinary and legal action for failing to follow mandated digital recording procedures and development rules. Non-compliance in processing redevelopment documents could lead to financial losses for the BMC, with strict adherence to SOPs now enforced.", "href": "https://realty.economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/regulatory/bmc-issues-disciplinary-warning-over-dangerous-building-management-in-mumbai/130042667?utm_source=newslisting&utm_medium=latestNews", "img": "data:image/png;base64, ", "img-src": "https://etimg.etb2bimg.com/thumb/img-size-75352/130042667.cms?width=150&height=112", "tag": "regulatory"}]}